[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      78[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # interesting but not strong evidence. These weights multiply with the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      79[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # NLP confidence score to produce a final evidence grade.
